# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

---

## Version 1.0.0 — Initial Release

### Added

- YOLO-based industrial defect detection
- Image inspection
- Camera inspection
- Video inspection
- Industrial defect engine
- Machine health scoring
- Machine status prediction
- Predictive maintenance planner
- Analytics dashboard
- Factory Digital Twin
- Machine records
- Inspection history
- AI Copilot (Ollama + Qwen)
- PDF inspection reports
- SQLite database integration
- SQLAlchemy ORM
- Streamlit user interface

---

## Planned (v1.1)

- Docker support
- GitHub Actions
- Logging
- Improved documentation
- Performance optimization

---

## Planned (v2.0)

- Authentication
